* Carnage snarled and spat, how dare this clone think that she was a 
Maximal!*

" I'm no Maximal, you dolt! My friend is! I'm neutral, for your 
information!"

* She snarls and whispers to herself...*

" And an assassin at that!"

* Carnage glares at Cyber Claw and bares her teeth at her.*

" And I wasn't following you, I accidentally ran into you while trying to 
find food! Does that answer your questions?!"
